ddf.catalog.content.plugin

Interface PreCreateStoragePlugin

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Checksum, PreviewStoragePlugin, SecurityLoggingPlugin

    public interface PreCreateStoragePlugin
    Services implementing this interface are called immediately before an item is created in the content repository.

    This code is experimental. While this interface is functional and tested, it may change or be removed in a future version of the library.
